-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/costa-says-recapitalization-of-domestic-banks-very-important-.html
European Central Bank Governing
Council member Carlos Costa said boosting the capital of
 Portugal ’s banks is “very important.”  “The recapitalization of the banking system is very
important,” Costa, who is the governor of the Bank of Portugal,
said during a speech in Lisbon today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
